# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Clock Crew — Local Environment Overrides
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  These values override secrets from Vault and vault/.env.
#  Only add variables you want to change for local development.
#
#  To use:  cp .env.example .env
#
#  Resolution order (first wins):
#    1. process.env (manual env vars)
#    2. This file (.env)
#    3. Vault service
#    4. Shared vault/.env fallback
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Server ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CLOCK_CREW_PORT="3001"

# ── Vault Connection ──────────────────────────────────────────
# VAULT_SERVICE_URL="http://<host>:5599"
# VAULT_SERVICE_TOKEN=""

# ── Service URLs ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# LUPOS_URL="http://localhost:1337"
# MINIO_INTERNAL_URL="http://<host>:9000"

# ── Sessions (visitor analytics) ─────────────────────────────
# SESSIONS_SERVICE_URL="http://localhost:5580"
# SESSIONS_SERVICE_PUBLIC_URL=""
